Install
Download file to /usr/local/src directory

cd /usr/local/src

curl -O <URL to download>

tar xfz s3cmd-1.6.1.tar.gz

Install python setuptools

yum install python-setuptools

Next install s3cmd

python setup.py install

Configure
Start command from user which will used in script or will use s3cmd

s3cmd --configure

Fill answers on questions.

Access key and Secret key are your identifiers for Amazon S3. Leave them empty for using the env variables.

Provide password for encrypt files.

Configuration will be saved to '$HOME/.s3cfg'

Checking
s3cmd ls <s3 URL>
